{"text_id":253452,"tokens":["Title",":"," An"," Experimental"," Test"," of"," Non","-","Local"," Realism","\n\n","Abstract",":","\n","In"," this"," study",","," we"," address"," the"," longstanding"," debate"," between"," quantum"," mechanics"," and"," classical"," interpretations"," of"," physical"," reality",","," specifically"," focusing"," on"," non","-","local"," realism","."," Non","-","local"," realism"," pos","its"," that"," particles"," can"," influence"," each"," other"," instantaneously"," over"," any"," distance",","," challenging"," the"," locality"," principle"," of"," classical"," physics","."," We"," aim"," to"," experimentally"," test"," the"," validity"," of"," non","-","local"," realism"," by"," employing"," a"," Bell"," test"," experiment"," with"," entangled"," photon"," pairs","."," Utilizing"," a"," high","-","efficiency"," photon"," source"," and"," state","-","of","-","the","-","art"," detectors",","," we"," measure"," the"," correlations"," between"," entangled"," photons"," under"," varying"," conditions","."," Our"," methodology"," involves"," rigorous"," statistical"," analysis"," to"," ensure"," the"," reliability"," and"," accuracy"," of"," the"," results","."," We"," observe"," that"," the"," experimental"," data"," violate"," Bell","'","s"," inequalities",","," thereby"," providing"," strong"," evidence"," against"," local"," realism","."," Furthermore",","," our"," results"," are"," consistent"," with"," the"," predictions"," of"," quantum"," mechanics",","," reinforcing"," the"," non","-","local"," nature"," of"," quantum"," entanglement","."," This"," work"," contributes"," to"," the"," broader"," understanding"," of"," quantum"," phenomena"," and"," has"," significant"," implications"," for"," the"," development"," of"," quantum"," technologies",","," such"," as"," quantum"," computing"," and"," secure"," communication"," systems","."," Our"," findings"," underscore"," the"," necessity"," of"," re","-","evalu","ating"," classical"," assumptions"," about"," the"," nature"," of"," reality"," in"," light"," of"," quantum"," theory","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"gpt4o","label":1}